channel.title: A very annoying Silabsoft v4 client error
channel.description:
Ok i downloaded Java 6u3.Got recognized by doing jdk1.6.0_02 or 03? idk Opened version4 with winrar Then clicked run.bat and it opens goes to login page type everything in then click login and suddenly closes and says:
C:\Documents and Settings\Nemat\Desktop>java -Xmx500m -jar client.jar 0 0 highme m members 0 RS2 user client - release #317 silabsoft.org # # An unexpected error has been detected by Java Runtime Environment: # # EXCEPTION_FLT_STACK_CHECK (0xc0000092) at pc=0x0093cea9, pid=1004, tid=2892 # # Java VM: Java HotSpot(TM) Client VM (1.6.0_03-b05 mixed mode, sharing) # Problematic frame: # v ~RuntimeStub::resolve_opt_virtual_call # # An error report file with more information is saved as hs_err_pid1004.log # # If you would like to submit a bug report, please visit: # http://java.sun.com/webapps/bugreport/crash.jsp #
C:\Documents and Settings\Nemat\Desktop>pause Press any key to continue . . .
